lead_paragraph: Green Bay Packers wide receiver Jordy Nelson, who has been trying to recover from a right knee injury that sidelined him in 2015, has tweaked his other knee leading the team to put him on the physically unable to perform (PUP) list.

headline.print_headline: Packers' Nelson Sidelined With Injury to Other Knee
headline.main: Packers' Nelson Sidelined With Injury to Other Knee
